      <title>美国对台湾公投抱有信心，警惕干涉</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-11/us-has-confidence-in-taiwan-vote-as-it-watches-for-interference</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一位高级政府官员表示，美国正在密切关注中国干预台湾即将举行的选举的任何迹象，但对台湾的民主进程充满信心。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-11/us-has-confidence-in-taiwan-vote-as-it-watches-for-interference</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Jan 2024 01:24:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>首尔表示，朝鲜将向俄罗斯发射新型导弹</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-11/north-korea-to-send-new-class-of-missiles-to-russia-seoul-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国国防部长表示，朝鲜正寻求通过向莫斯科发送新型战术导弹来加强与俄罗斯的军事合作，而平壤可能很快就会对其自己的旨在实施核打击的导弹进行新的测试。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-11/north-korea-to-send-new-class-of-missiles-to-russia-seoul-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Jan 2024 01:10:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>全球一半 GDP 进入选举年，哪些因素面临风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/graphics/2024-global-election-watch-on-economic-market-issues/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国、英国、印度、台湾和南非的选举是投资者最关注经济和市场波动的政治竞赛之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/graphics/2024-global-election-watch-on-economic-market-issues/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Jan 2024 23:00:13 GMT</pubDate>
